From: cara <caradove@...>
Subject: [unschoolingbasics] Is anyone in the Columbus OH area?
To: unschoolingbasics@yahoogroups.com
Date: Wednesday, May 12, 2010, 1:51 PM


 



Hi,

I am studying a five day intensive course in Columbus in June and we live two hours away in Wheeling WV. Some of you who were at the waterpark might know us!

Well it is far to be away from family and I am not sure whether to travel the two hours each way every day. So I wondered if any unschoolers would want to meet up with my husband and kids to play some of the time, so he could be near by so I can see/ nurse our 1yo. Or even whether any folks we know might be happy for me to stay with them and I could maybe set up a babysitting arrangement for my 1yo with an unschooler teen? Just throwing ideas out there!!

Let me know!

Cara, husband is Bala (anyone know him from SSUDS?)
